data.description: SELLER HAS REDUCED THE PRICE!!!  Home on LARGE CORNER LOT with mature landscaping located in the established gated community of Dinner Lake Shores. This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath, split floor plan solar enhanced home is family ready. The double front door entry welcomes you to the great room with a wood-burning fireplace, plant shelves, and a vaulted ceiling. This area is open to the kitchen featuring a snack bar, quartz countertops, a new sink, stainless steel appliances, natural gas range, a new microwave, a walk-in pantry, and an eating area overlooking your side yard.  Three bedrooms share a bathroom on one side of the home while the master bedroom has its own area with an ensuite bathroom with a garden tub, separate shower, and water closet divided by a walk-in closet. The  lanai has been enclosed to make a nice Florida room with an added ceiling fan. The home has been recently painted inside and out. The laundry room features a stacked washer and dryer and a storage cupboard. Other amenities are tankless natural gas heated water, new garage door opener, a fenced backyard, irrigation with a well, new ceiling fans, tile and laminate floors, community playground. community sidewalks.  Close to shopping, restaurants, schools, and medical facilities.  Centrally located in Florida. About 90 minutes from coastal beaches, one hour to theme parks in Orlando, 15 minutes to Legoland, and 10 minutes to beautiful Bok Tower.
